flowchart LR
    Start["🚀 Start Session"] --> Evaluate["🔍 Evaluate Target<br/>Probe + analyze + assess + identify"]
    Evaluate --> Select["🎰 Select Tool<br/>Use findings + weight next action"]
    Select --> Execute["⚡ Execute Tool<br/>CPU/memory spike, cluster, MTD rotation"]
    Execute --> Record["📝 Record Metrics<br/>Capture outcomes + telemetry"]
    Record --> Broadcast["📡 Broadcast Results"]
    Broadcast --> Wait["⏳ Wait Interval"]
    Wait --> Decision{"Continue?"}
    Decision -->|Yes| Evaluate
    Decision -->|No| Complete["✅ Session Complete<br/>📊 Generate Report"]
